    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <p>During execution of <b>“User selects build your own investment Options for Enrollment of Individual Account with BYO and One-Time Bank Contribution Option”</b> for <b>NJD plan</b>, failure is observed due to <b>recent changes in Investment Portfolio page UI/content</b>.</p>

<p>Because of this change, <b>funds that are active in DB (web_status='A') and present in CSV test data are not displayed in UI</b>, leading to validation failure.</p>

<hr />

<h3><a name="Environment%3A"></a><b>Environment:</b></h3>

<ul>
	<li>Application: Universal Enrollment</li>
	<li>Plan: NJD (NJBEST 529)</li>
	<li>Flow: BYO Investment Selection</li>
	<li>Environment: Stage</li>
	<li>Report:<br/>
<a href="https://ascensus-gs.gitlab.io/-/products/depot/qa-automation/prime-test-automation/-/jobs/15025513865/artifacts/unite/unite-universal-enrollment/target/surefire-reports/njd.20260625011234781.UniversalEnrollmentPositive.feature_html_chrome_failedresult.html" class="external-link" rel="nofollow noreferrer">https://ascensus-gs.gitlab.io/-/products/depot/qa-automation/prime-test-automation/-/jobs/15025513865/artifacts/unite/unite-universal-enrollment/target/surefire-reports/njd.20260625011234781.UniversalEnrollmentPositive.feature_html_chrome_failedresult.html</a></li>
</ul>


<hr />

<h3><a name="StepstoReproduce%3A"></a><b>Steps to Reproduce:</b></h3>

<ol>
	<li>Start NJD Individual Account enrollment</li>
	<li>Select <b>Build Your Own (BYO)</b></li>
	<li>Proceed with <b>One-Time Bank Contribution</b></li>
	<li>Navigate to <b>Select Portfolios page</b></li>
	<li>Compare UI portfolios with DB/CSV data</li>
</ol>


<hr />

<h3><a name="ActualResult%3A"></a><b>Actual Result:</b></h3>

<ul>
	<li>❌ Investment portfolio page structure/content is changed</li>
	<li>❌ Multiple active funds (from DB &amp; CSV) are <b>not shown in UI</b></li>
	<li>❌ Only partial portfolios displayed (Target portfolios + limited Objective-based portfolios)</li>
</ul>


<p>Error:</p>

<div class="preformatted panel" style="border-width: 1px;"><div class="preformattedContent panelContent">
<pre>java.lang.AssertionError: Funds in database (web_status='A') but not shown in UE:
[Franklin U.S. Government Money 529 Portfolio,
 NJ Treasury-Managed Portfolio A,
 NJ Treasury-Managed Portfolio B,
 NJ Treasury-Managed Portfolio C,
 NJ Treasury-Managed Portfolio D,
 NJ Treasury-Managed Portfolio E,
 New Jersey Treasury-Managed Better Educational Savings Portfolio]
</pre>
</div></div>

<hr />

<h3><a name="ExpectedResult%3A"></a><b>Expected Result:</b></h3>

<ul>
	<li>✅ Investment portfolio page should display <b>all active funds (web_status='A')</b></li>
	<li>✅ UI should be consistent with DB and CSV test data</li>
	<li>✅ No unintended filtering due to UI changes</li>
</ul>


<hr />

<h3><a name="Evidence%3A"></a><b>Evidence:</b></h3>

<ul>
	<li><b>DB:</b> Active funds exist (verified with fund IDs and allocation data)</li>
	<li><b>CSV:</b> Expected funds present in test data</li>
</ul>

